The Telegraph - Calcutta : Business

 Khaitan focus on taxation

 A STAFF REPORTER

 Calcutta, Dec. 19: Khaitan and Co, one of the oldest law firms in the country headquartered here, is aggressively tapping the market potential of various legal services and has taken up a number of ambitious projects. 

 An official said the company is focussing on taxation and legal outsourcing, as it sees a huge potential there.

 It has a strong team on indirect taxes and is now building a similar one on the direct tax front. We aim to provide customers with top quality tax advisory and litigation support services.

 To build a strong team on taxation, the company has hired a number of tax experts. 




